{"tid":1361480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府電話簿中有關克警的資料突然消失","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T16:35:52.000Z","uid":54442,"like":71,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"372766b78c5cb73bf58a04d5347d4ef296e1136d","tid":1361480,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:20:54.000Z","msg":"突然發現克警將成個部門嘅小隊負責人名字及電話完全刪除（例如以下截圖）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3h0ycGZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3h0ycGZ.png&h=7ee7b05b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n更新日期是7月24日，做埋呢啲小動作，屌你丫！<br />\n<br />\n但係，呢個世界有偉大的google 頁庫存檔成為「小氣簿」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O5n8L2w.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO5n8L2w.png&h=54462341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位清趁google未再有更新資料庫時快點去尋寶吧！<br />\n<br />\n報告完畢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07de0575197f3357be307e7444e6d2fe73e117bd","tid":1361480,"uid":54442,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:22:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb9eba904911f0cd7e282ff9b51c6c63c02dfadd","tid":1361480,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"有無高手爬蟲爬晒所有內容做對照 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc9d372fc6266f613d492ea466e88518af07439","tid":1361480,"uid":191290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"855e6d8c439993dbf434817c1699092e08b89257","tid":1361480,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eb9eba904911f0cd7e282ff9b51c6c63c02dfadd","tid":1361480,"uid":164374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"有無高手爬蟲爬晒所有內容做對照 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:50.000Z","msg":"講漏咗如何使用搜尋關鍵字：<br />\n<br />\n搜尋已知部門/分組名稱 （例如我用了反恐特勤隊做例子），再加 職位 （例如我用了督察做例子）<br />\n<br />\nGoogle就應該會出到有關政府電話簿的記錄，再選頁庫存檔就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一起儲定文攻彈藥啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab44aaf7767601d0b778eadf8337c8348f6dc83a","tid":1361480,"uid":54442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:38:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5b53117b9c0816c030a8d086c1ec5f3ad7e9570d","tid":1361480,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:39:55.000Z","msg":"除咗警區高層，連cid/軍裝幫辦名都冇show出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8ce9489d432128fc1e587bec0adf06580502214","tid":1361480,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:40:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n作惡多端真係連個天都唔會幫你"},{"pid":"65e55bc49bd281c11f7633c32bf727f5a280a3b4","tid":1361480,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"748553971f4dfeb55af491e4643edc630203585f","tid":1361480,"uid":5191,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:42:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"963cb1ef29a42fef1e361058f8b7bbd0983f535b","tid":1361480,"uid":5191,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"5b53117b9c0816c030a8d086c1ec5f3ad7e9570d","tid":1361480,"uid":21139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"ci